	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001222_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right">18 Hart St.</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">Bloomsbury</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">11<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> Feby 1858</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Sir</p>
<lb/><p>It will give 
<lb/>me great pleasure 
<lb/>to be the bearer of 
<lb/>a present to <persName>Sekeletu</persName>
<lb/>and also to <persName>Shinte</persName>
<lb/>if I come as I 
<lb/>possibly may into 
<lb/>his country. And 
<lb/>to express the kind 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001222_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>interest you feel 
<lb/>in his welfare<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I shall ever esteem 
<lb/>the gospel of Christ 
<lb/>as the greatest 
<lb/>boon I can confer 
<lb/>on the Africans<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>It is the solace of 
<lb/>my own soul 
<lb/>and while devoting 
<lb/>myself to opening 
<lb/>up the country 
<lb/>to the sympathies 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001222_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>of Christians it is 
<lb/>only with a view 
<lb/>of extending the 
<lb/>kingdom of our 
<lb/>Lord more extensively<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>The people make 
<lb/>thick milk and 
<lb/>no cheese but it 
<lb/>tastes like that 
<lb/>article. If they 
<lb/>taste cheese it is 
<lb/>with faces of 
<lb/>infinite disgust.</p>
<lb/><p>I have had no 
<lb/>time to write more 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001222_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'--> 
<lb/>for the press and 
<lb/>dislike composition<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>Thanking you 
<lb/>kindly &amp; heartily 
<lb/>for you letter 
<lb/>and its enclosure </p>
<lb/><p>I am &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p>David Livingstone</p>
<lb/><p><persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Bathurst Woodman</persName></p>
			
</div>
